tab1.text1: Get back here any time by pressing F1 on PC or using the radial menu on console. You can find important server information here. This server is open to PC, Playstation, and Xbox players. If you have nice respectful friends you can invite them.
tab1.text2:
<TextStyle.LightBlue>-The Library:</> 43 Lat 69 Long. A place for us to share recipies. Includes powered crafting stations.

*Message LadyMourg on Discord to add community locations. Please provide the location name, brief description, and coordinates.
tab1.text3:
<TextStyle.LightBlue>CURRENT EVENT:</> Winter Wonderland (12/21-1/7)

<TextStyle.LightBlue>-12/24/2023:</>Based on player feedback, turned eels into otters. Jellyfish are back in. Fixed code so Titanosaurs should be out as intended. Giant bee honey should now stack.
